description: Verify a flodl export by loading it through HF Python's AutoModelFor* and forwarding bit-exact vs the Hub source. Auto-detects family + head from <dir>/config.json (model_type + architectures[0]).

# Argv passes through to the Python script (entry: commands forward argv;
# run: commands do not — see feedback_cli_docs_three_contexts).
#
# Pipeline shape:
#   fdl flodl-hf export       --hub <repo>  --out <dir>   # dev container
#   fdl flodl-hf verify-export <dir>                       # hf-parity container
#
# Hub source recovery order (verify_export.py):
#   1. --hub-source <repo> override (positional flag passthrough)
#   2. config.json `flodl_source_repo` field (stamped by `export --hub`)
#   3. config.json `_name_or_path` (rare; HF strips it on most repos)
#   4. loud error pointing at --hub-source

docker: hf-parity
entry: python /workspace/flodl-hf/scripts/verify_export.py
